Class TrialDao

java.lang.Object
  selrach.bnetbuilder.data.TrialDao

public class TrialDao
extends java.lang.Object

This is the trial data access object. It can manage multiple DataAccessors so that only this object is needed to work with multiple data sources

Charles Robertson

Sets up the evidence present in a trial on each of the variables they have been mapped to

Parameters:

announce - should this trigger an update to the world that evidence has changed? This should probably be false if you are running an algorithm that relys on data (such as learning) so that we don't waste cpu cycles updating all the listeners
Returns:
